## Tips for picking the 20

- Sort by reaction count, not impressions. Reactions correlate with
  voice resonance; impressions correlate with timing and luck.
- Include posts across formats (text-only, with image, with video,
  with carousel). The agent learns shape, not just words.
- Don't filter out "weird" posts that did well · those are usually
  your strongest voice fingerprints.
- Drop pure repost / share-with-comment posts. They don't reflect
  your original writing.
